International
Indian designer Manish Malhotra showcased his latest collection
dubbed Sensual Affair at an invite only affair at Two Rivers
Mall in Nairobi.  The event was exclusively sponsored by
Victoria Commercial Bank, who treated their special clients to a
fashionable experience.  The runway show featured 26 Kenyan models from
Mochez Models and 15 international models from India.  Top Bollywood
actress Kareena Kapoor all graced the runway as the showstopper of
the event.
